track_notes: I did more than one activation using my mountain bike. When i arrived at the Col Notre Dame, where plenty cars are parked, i used the forest road to the point of vue, you can use the foot path (did it in 2015) whitch is fine; take some water. As you cannot get in the trig point (restricted area) you can setup antenna next the road in activation zone.
I used my vtt for fun! at the beginning, the road is private, i had to wait someone get in the park!!! then the place is wonderfull.
